{"tid":20603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的今日撞到女神","createTime":"2016-12-03T12:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T17:09:07.000Z","uid":9601,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5757471229ccb52acd584b8ccb9e1e16246c98b7","tid":20603,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:38:45.000Z","msg":"「起身啦衰仔，成日都唔知醒返學。」<br />\n<br />\n聽到依句我就即刻彈左起身，你以為我係比我媽子大叫聲吵醒？你錯啦，我係比佢放係我頭上雪過濕毛巾整醒，仲要係冬天，唉....<br />\n<br />\n我用九秒八七速度換衫拎住媽子整好嘅三文治衝左出門口。點解係九秒八七？因為我係異於常人，九秒九每個人都可以做到，實在太垃圾。哈！<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，我叫陳子樂，係一個普普通通既中五生。仆街唔記得帶書包。<br />\n<br />\n「陳子樂，你今日係就係冇遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但你個書包呢？」佢就係我班主任<br />\n<br />\n「上次你就PE衫加皮鞋，今次你就唔就得帶書包，你個腦去左邊？姐係欠交功課啦，今日留堂罰抄。」<br />\n<br />\n「咪去左屎忽到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」佢就係我老死，李魯明。<br />\n<br />\n「我..唉」<br />\n<br />\n突然有一股仙氣漂過<br />\n<br />\n「嘩女神啊」成班都係冇用嘅垃圾兵仔。<br />\n<br />\n「啤咩啊？死臭雞」我當然冇講出口，其實佢都係我女神。唉<br />\n<br />\n「無驚無險又到六點，留完堂走人，miss 88。」我好快就衝左出去<br />\n<br />\n就係轉角位撞到女神<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點算好？女神比我撞到飛左落樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求救，我冇錢賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91ccc7eb05b0a4d77871832eabaea534452aa82","tid":20603,"uid":32612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:41:49.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7be6ced4098a9aaeb760b1f2955ab9ec3c467c","tid":20603,"uid":26787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出多啲"},{"pid":"d4451eb8e51bed2f854d5f869007400275706b2d","tid":20603,"uid":7021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"以身相許"},{"pid":"badb0911455d1b2084a8e972372c30fca9cb674e","tid":20603,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出多啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩野出多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求救文黎"},{"pid":"8ebe369d448fe71307a1de3789b83ee7ce816e07","tid":20603,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以身相許</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想以身相許<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6835f5c8e5a315df1b26f11fce7b80d1a8b2171","tid":20603,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"又冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}